{"tid":2323436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咩話 元朝滿人屠殺左6700萬中國人 點解冇元朝大屠殺紀念日？","createTime":"2020-12-13T07:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T08:24:13.000Z","uid":42246,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9a5b09503181b2bda1ea3d3e96c0104a89bd6d9d","tid":2323436,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"蒙古帝國屠殺、滅族記錄<br />\n這次屠殺空前絕後，已載入世界吉尼斯記錄。<br />\n<br />\n估計中國直接死於屠殺的有6700萬。連同中亞西亞和東歐共死亡約2億人。<br />\n<br />\n蒙古人滅花剌子模，屠尋思幹（撒馬爾罕）城約百萬人口；滅西夏，屠銀川八十餘萬。蒙古人數次西征，凡有抵抗即屠城，共屠數百城，包括屠殺了巴格達的數十萬人口，整個中亞一片廢墟。<br />\n<br />\n1122年全國人口9347萬，到元初1274年，人口887萬。損失率高達91%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n滿人依家重霸佔中原之地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n昭昭前事，惕惕後人！歲末寒冬，祭奠同胞！ ​勿忘國恥，吾輩自強！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede14349f47a3952314e1b8226d79621fd79df67","tid":2323436,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:39:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff38521ee69fab50785863839453970f7f00fe20","tid":2323436,"uid":24730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:42:38.000Z","msg":"清朝都有揚州十日嘉定三屠"},{"pid":"6c83535ba7f4c18c208f803f132429a6c94f5c82","tid":2323436,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:43:53.000Z","msg":"太平天國都屠殺過南京人"},{"pid":"5cafc82d725cd9a6db6b7d53648f325f221d01bb","tid":2323436,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T07:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"